Reasoning: The paper discusses the practical implementation of a company-wide methodology to minimize the risk of undesired consequences of AI, which falls under the category of responsible AI. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI. The paper also touches upon issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and fairness (cs.CR), which are important considerations in the development and deployment of AI systems. Additionally, the paper discusses the organizational and technical aspects of implementing responsible AI, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
